UPSTREAM DATA NOTICE
===============================================================================

Derived intermediate data in data/*.csv originates from:
 - Tabula Muris Senis (Schaum et al. 2020; figshare 12654728) — CC-BY 4.0
 - Kimmel et al. 2019 (Genome Research; GEO GSE132901) — paper terms
 - Calico rat aging atlas (Zou et al. 2022, GEO GSE141784) — paper terms
 - Pythia-410M (EleutherAI, HuggingFace) — Apache 2.0

Derived data is shared under CC-BY 4.0 with upstream attribution required.
Do not redistribute raw h5ad files from those sources in this repository;
always obtain them from the official upstream location and cite
accordingly.
